reviewText: In the pictures it showed that it was uncensored and rated X but when I got it it was Unrated and censored. I was mad but it was ok for a doc. Still don't recommend if you thought what I did.
Didn't like it. No my cup of tea. Scenes were covered or blocked. It was actually boring. Wouldn't give more than one star.

if you are interested in making money in adult entertainment industry this movie will give you a very human look backstage behind the smoke and mirrors. no five star because the movie spends so much time on tormenting this girl and very little on what she could do succed in life and love.

i wish someone would show the good AND the bad. relationships and love didn't even come into the picture. how can i feel for the main female lead in the movie when the chick admits that all she is looking foe is easy money. where is the love?
